---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="umbrai - On-Device AI Privacy Protection | GDPR Compliance for EU Businesses"
  description="Prevent data disclosure to LLMs with on-device anonymization. GDPR-compliant AI privacy protection for European businesses. Secure your sensitive data before it leaves your machine."
  canonical="https://umbrai.xyz"
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section
    class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center px-6"
    style="background-color: #F2F2F2;"
  >
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <!-- Subtle geometric divider -->
      <div class="flex justify-center mb-8" role="presentation">
        <img
          src="/half-circle.svg"
          alt="Decorative geometric divider"
          class="max-w-full max-h-12 w-full h-auto object-contain"
          style="max-width: 300px;"
          loading="eager"
        />
      </div>

      <h1
        class="text-6xl md:text-7xl font-light mb-6 tracking-tight"
        style="color: #000000;"
      >
        umbrai
      </h1>

      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-8 font-light" style="color: #000000;">
        On-Device AI Privacy Protection
      </h2>

      <p
        class="text-xl mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed"
        style="color: #000000;"
      >
        Prevent inadvertent data disclosure to LLMs with on-device anonymization
        that ensures GDPR compliance before data ever leaves your machine.
      </p>

      <a
        href="mailto:hello@umbrai.xyz?subject=Interest in Umbrai&body=Hi, I'm interested in learning more about Umbrai."
        class="inline-block px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-medium hover:opacity-90 transition-all"
        style="background-color: #000000; color: #F2F2F2;"
        aria-label="Contact us about Umbrai privacy protection"
      >
        Get in Touch
      </a>

      <p class="text-sm mt-4" style="color: #000000; opacity: 0.7;">
        cross-platform app coming soon
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Evolving Landscape of LLM Privacy Risks -->
  <section
    id="risks"
    class="py-24 text-white"
    style="background-color: #000000;"
  >
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h3 class="text-3xl font-light mb-8" style="color: #F2F2F2;">
        The Evolving Landscape of LLM Privacy Risks
      </h3>

      <p class="text-xl mb-16 leading-relaxed" style="color: #F2F2F2;">
        The European Data Protection Board identifies critical privacy
        vulnerabilities across the entire AI lifecycle.
      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <!-- Input Data Risks -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div
            class="w-16 h-16 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6"
            style="background-color: #D9EAFD;"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-8 h-8"
              style="color: #000000;"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M7 16a4 4 0 01-.88-7.903A5 5 0 1115.9 6L16 6a5 5 0 011 9.9M9 19l3 3m0 0l3-3m-3 3V10"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-lg font-medium mb-3" style="color: #F2F2F2;">
            Input Data Risks
          </h4>
          <p style="color: #F2F2F2; opacity: 0.8;">
            Users inadvertently send sensitive personal or corporate data in
            prompts, risking exposure, over-collection, and misuse by
            third-party AI services.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Output Data Risks -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div
            class="w-16 h-16 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6"
            style="background-color: #D9EAFD;"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-8 h-8"
              style="color: #000000;"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M7 16a4 4 0 01-.88-7.903A5 5 0 1115.9 6L16 6a5 5 0 011 9.9M15 13l-3-3m0 0l-3 3m3-3v12"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-lg font-medium mb-3" style="color: #F2F2F2;">
            Output Data Risks
          </h4>
          <p style="color: #F2F2F2; opacity: 0.8;">
            LLMs can memorize and regenerate sensitive information from training
            data or infer new personal details through linkage attacks and
            fabrication.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Training Data Risks -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div
            class="w-16 h-16 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6"
            style="background-color: #D9EAFD;"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-8 h-8"
              style="color: #000000;"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M4 7v10c0 2.21 3.582 4 8 4s8-1.79 8-4V7M4 7c0 2.21 3.582 4 8 4s8-1.79 8-4M4 7c0-2.21 3.582-4 8-4s8 1.79 8 4m0 5c0 2.21-3.582 4-8 4s-8-1.79-8-4"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-lg font-medium mb-3" style="color: #F2F2F2;">
            Training Data Risks
          </h4>
          <p style="color: #F2F2F2; opacity: 0.8;">
            Personal data is often included in training sets without a valid
            legal basis, leading to significant compliance and bias issues.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Security Risks -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div
            class="w-16 h-16 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6"
            style="background-color: #D9EAFD;"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-8 h-8"
              style="color: #000000;"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-lg font-medium mb-3" style="color: #F2F2F2;">
            Security Risks
          </h4>
          <p style="color: #F2F2F2; opacity: 0.8;">
            Vulnerabilities like prompt injection attacks can be used to
            manipulate LLMs and exfiltrate sensitive, confidential information.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How It Works -->
  <section
    id="solution"
    class="py-24 relative overflow-hidden"
    style="background-color: #F2F2F2;"
  >
    <!-- Background Logo -->
    <div
      class="absolute top-1/2 right-10 transform -translate-y-1/2 pointer-events-none"
    >
      <img
        src="/logo-bg.svg"
        alt=""
        class="w-96 opacity-10 rotate-12"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center relative z-10">
      <h3 class="text-3xl font-light mb-16" style="color: #000000;">
        Privacy by Design: On-Device Protection
      </h3>

      <div
        class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm mb-8"
        style="background-color: #F2F2F2;"
      >
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm mb-3" style="color: #000000;">
              What the user types:
            </p>
            <div
              class="px-6 py-4 rounded-lg border text-left"
              style="background-color: #F2F2F2; border-color: #000000; color: #000000;"
            >
              "Review contract for <strong
                >patient John Smith (DOB: 15/03/1980)</strong
              > regarding <strong>€25,000</strong> treatment at <strong
                >Munich Medical Center</strong
              >, account <strong>DE89370400440532013000</strong>"
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex justify-center">
            <div
              class="text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium"
              style="background-color: #000000;"
            >
              Umbrai Anonymizes On-Device
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <p class="text-sm mb-3" style="color: #000000;">
              What AI services receive:
            </p>
            <div
              class="px-6 py-4 rounded-lg border text-left"
              style="background-color: #F2F2F2; border-color: #000000; color: #000000;"
            >
              "Review contract for <span
                class="px-1 rounded"
                style="background-color: #D9EAFD; color: #000000;"
                >[PATIENT_NAME]</span
              > regarding <span
                class="px-1 rounded"
                style="background-color: #D9EAFD; color: #000000;"
                >[AMOUNT]</span
              > treatment at <span
                class="px-1 rounded"
                style="background-color: #D9EAFD; color: #000000;"
                >[FACILITY]</span
              >, account <span
                class="px-1 rounded"
                style="background-color: #D9EAFD; color: #000000;"
                >[IBAN_MASKED]</span
              >"
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12" style="color: #000000;">
        Sensitive data never leaves your machine in its original form. LLMs
        receive only anonymized data, preventing memorization and ensuring GDPR
        compliance.
      </p>

      <!-- Dashboard Preview -->
      <div class="mt-16">
        <h4 class="text-xl font-light mb-8 text-center" style="color: #000000;">
          Monitor & Control Everything
        </h4>

        <div
          class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg border"
          style="border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);"
        >
          <!-- Dashboard Header -->
          <div
            class="text-left mb-6 pb-4 border-b"
            style="border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);"
          >
            <h3 class="text-xl font-light" style="color: #000000;">
              Umbrai Dashboard Example
            </h3>
            <p class="text-sm mt-1" style="color: #000000; opacity: 0.6;">
              Real-time privacy protection monitoring
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Status & Metrics -->
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-6">
            <!-- Status -->
            <div
              class="p-4 rounded-lg text-center"
              style="background-color: #000000;"
            >
              <div class="text-sm font-medium mb-2" style="color: #F2F2F2;">
                Status
              </div>
              <div
                class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full inline-block mb-2"
                style="background-color: #D9EAFD; color: #000000;"
              >
                ● Active
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Data Protected -->
            <div
              class="p-4 rounded-lg text-center"
              style="background-color: #F2F2F2; border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);"
            >
              <div class="text-sm font-medium mb-2" style="color: #000000;">
                Data Protected
              </div>
              <div class="text-lg font-light" style="color: #000000;">
                3.4 GB
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Last Activity -->
            <div
              class="p-4 rounded-lg text-center"
              style="background-color: #F2F2F2; border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);"
            >
              <div class="text-sm font-medium mb-2" style="color: #000000;">
                Last Activity
              </div>
              <div class="text-sm" style="color: #000000;">10:30 AM</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Protected Apps -->
          <div class="mb-4">
            <div class="text-sm font-medium mb-3" style="color: #000000;">
              Protected Apps
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span
                class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs"
                style="background-color: #D9EAFD; color: #000000;">Chrome</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs"
                style="background-color: #D9EAFD; color: #000000;">ChatGPT</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs"
                style="background-color: #D9EAFD; color: #000000;">Gmail</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs"
                style="background-color: #D9EAFD; color: #000000;">Cursor</span
              >
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Recent Activity Preview -->
          <div>
            <div class="text-sm font-medium mb-3" style="color: #000000;">
              Recent Activity
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <div
                class="p-3 rounded-lg text-sm"
                style="background-color: #F2F2F2; border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);"
              >
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                  <span style="color: #000000;">ChatGPT session protected</span>
                  <span
                    class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full"
                    style="background-color: #D9EAFD; color: #000000;">✓</span
                  >
                </div>
              </div>
              <div
                class="p-3 rounded-lg text-sm"
                style="background-color: #F2F2F2; border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);"
              >
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                  <span style="color: #000000;">Gmail compose protected</span>
                  <span
                    class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full"
                    style="background-color: #D9EAFD; color: #000000;">✓</span
                  >
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- View Dashboard Link -->
          <div
            class="text-center mt-6 pt-4 border-t"
            style="border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);"
          >
            <a
              href="/dashboard"
              class="inline-block px-6 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity"
              style="background-color: #000000; color: #F2F2F2;"
            >
              View Full Example Dashboard →
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Benefits Section -->
  <section id="benefits" class="py-24" style="background-color: #000000;">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h3 class="text-3xl font-light text-center mb-16" style="color: #F2F2F2;">
        EDPB-Aligned Privacy Protection
      </h3>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div
            class="w-16 h-16 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6"
            style="background-color: #D9EAFD;"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-8 h-8"
              style="color: #000000;"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M9 3v2m6-2v2M9 19v2m6-2v2M5 9H3m2 6H3m18-6h-2m2 6h-2M7 19h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2zM9 9h6v6H9V9z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-medium mb-4" style="color: #F2F2F2;">
            Data Minimization
          </h4>
          <p style="color: #F2F2F2;">
            Only anonymized data reaches LLM providers, implementing data
            minimization at the source
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div
            class="w-16 h-16 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6"
            style="background-color: #D9EAFD;"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-8 h-8"
              style="color: #000000;"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-medium mb-4" style="color: #F2F2F2;">
            Real-time Anonymization
          </h4>
          <p style="color: #F2F2F2;">
            Automatic detection and masking of PII, PHI, financial data, and
            custom keywords
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div
            class="w-16 h-16 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6"
            style="background-color: #D9EAFD;"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-8 h-8"
              style="color: #000000;"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-medium mb-4" style="color: #F2F2F2;">
            Compliance Audit Trail
          </h4>
          <p style="color: #F2F2F2;">
            Local audit logs confirm when anonymization occurred for GDPR
            compliance documentation
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact Form -->
  <section class="py-24" style="background-color: #F2F2F2;">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <a
        href="mailto:hello@umbrai.xyz?subject=Interest in Umbrai&body=Hi, I'm interested in learning more about Umbrai."
        class="inline-block px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-medium hover:opacity-90 transition-all"
        style="background-color: #000000; color: #F2F2F2;"
      >
        Get in Touch
      </a>

      <p class="text-sm mt-4" style="color: #000000; opacity: 0.7;">
        cross-platform app coming soon.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer
    class="py-3 border-t"
    style="background-color: #F2F2F2; border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);"
  >
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <p class="text-xs" style="color: #000000; opacity: 0.5;">
        © 2025 umbrai
      </p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>
